# 🎯 PHISH-SHIELD

A browser-based phishing email detector that analyzes social engineering tactics, flags suspicious URLs, and scores email risk in real-time.

## 🚀 Live Demo

https://adamanuhu-star.github.io/phish-shield

## 📊 Features

- **Social Engineering Detection** — Identifies urgency, fear, greed, and authority tactics
- **Sender Analysis** — Spots spoofed domains, homograph attacks, suspicious TLDs
- **URL Inspection** — Flags bit.ly links, suspicious TLDs, numeric domains
- **Content Analysis** — Detects credential requests, poor grammar, excessive caps
- **Risk Scoring** — 0-100 phishing probability with actionable recommendations
- **TCP/IP Stack Visualization** — See how packets traverse network layers

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5, Tailwind CSS, Vanilla JavaScript
- No external dependencies
- No data transmitted externally

## 🎯 Security Concepts Demonstrated

- **Social Engineering:** Understanding manipulation tactics used in phishing
- **Email Authentication:** SPF, DKIM, DMARC awareness through sender analysis
- **URL Analysis:** TLD reputation, homograph attacks, link obfuscation
- **Threat Intelligence:** Pattern matching against known phishing indicators

